DoubleKeyHashmap

It's a hashmap (aka namespace) which uses two string keys.  It uses CBA namespace as base.  Implementation is not ideal because it just combines two keys into one with a separator between them, so in theory there might be conflicts, but it's fine for now.

Author: Sparker 22 August 2019

Functions
set

Sets value associated with key0-key1 pair.

Parameters: _k0, _k1, _value

_k0

String, Key 0

_k1

String, Key 1

_value

anything, the value to set

Returns: nil
